    "(\"marker_approach\", \"stop\", \"marker_approach\")"
  ],
  "strategy": [
    "Advance forward when clear, using a commit state to ensure action completion.",
    "On front obstacle, escape by backing up or rotating fully; do not allow immediate forward movement after obstacle.",
    "On left or right obstacle, rotate away from obstacle using commit states to avoid oscillation.",
    "Commit states ensure the robot completes a rotation or forward move before reevaluating.",
    "When marker is seen, switch to marker_approach and use move_to_marker until close; stop when close.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state to ensure reactivity.",
    "No state allows both clockwise and counterclockwise rotation as controllable actions, preventing oscillation.",
    "Helper states (escape_backup, marker_approach) manage recovery and goal approach safely."
  ]
}